1. Plane Old Weather Source-Available License (software)
================================================================================

This Section 1 governs the "Software": all source code, configuration, and
tooling in this repository — everything under model/, web/ (excluding the
written content and figures covered by Section 2), deploy/, and docs/.

1.1 Definitions.
    "Bow Echo LLC" (also "we" / "us") is the copyright holder and licensor.
    "You" is any individual or entity exercising rights under this License.
    "Public Deployment" means hosting, serving, publishing, providing access to,
    or otherwise making available the Software or any derivative or modified
    version of it — in whole or in part — to any third party over a network, the
    internet, or any public or external domain or service (including, without
    limitation, as a website, hosted application, or API). Building and running
    the Software on your own machine, or on a private network for your own
    personal, educational, evaluation, research, or development use, is NOT
    Public Deployment.

1.2 Grant. Subject to Your compliance with this License, Bow Echo LLC grants You
    a worldwide, royalty-free, non-exclusive, non-transferable license to:
      (a) access, view, and study the Software;
      (b) reproduce and fork the Software;
      (c) create modifications and derivative works of the Software; and
      (d) build, run, and use the Software and Your modifications locally and
          privately for personal, educational, evaluation, research, and
          development purposes.

1.3 Restriction — no public deployment. You MAY NOT engage in Public Deployment
    of the Software, or of any derivative or modified version of it, without the
    prior written permission of Bow Echo LLC. This is the central term of this
    License. For clarity, and without limiting the foregoing: You may not deploy
    this project, or a fork of it, to any public website, domain, subdomain,
    hosting platform, or content-delivery network — whether or not for
    commercial purposes, and whether or not you charge for access — without that
    prior written permission.

1.4 Redistribution. You may redistribute copies and forks of the Software,
    modified or unmodified, provided that (a) You do not engage in Public
    Deployment, (b) this License — including this Section 1 and the rationale
    above — is included intact, and (c) the copyright notice is preserved.

1.5 Reservation of rights. All rights not expressly granted in this Section 1 are
    reserved by Bow Echo LLC. No trademark, service mark, or branding rights are
    granted.

1.6 Termination. Any Public Deployment, or any other use outside the grant in
    Section 1.2, automatically terminates the rights granted to You under this
    Section 1. Rights may be reinstated only in writing by Bow Echo LLC.

